title: Presidential Nominations Sent to the Senate, 4-30-09 | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House




April 30, 2009

 



Presidential Nominations Sent to the Senate, 4-30-09




THE WHITE HOUSE   Office of the Press Secretary   FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE                                   April 30, 2009  NOMINATION SENT TO THE SENATE: Charles A. Blanchard, of Arizona, to be General Counsel of the Department of the Air Force, vice Mary L. Walker, resigned.
